---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
  <article class="prose">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-5">About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Toheeb, I build software systems that scale and AI tools that make things smarter. My background is in backend engineering and data-driven development and I like writing clean, efficient code to solve tricky problems.
    </p>

    <p>
      My guiding principle is: Freedom and Stewardship.
    </p>
    <p>
      Freedom covers time, choice, and curiosity.
    </p>
    <p>
      Stewardship captures responsibility without ego, building things that last, and leaving systems better than I found them.
    </p>
    <p>
      This blog is my personal corner on the internet. Enjoy 🎉
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
      You can reach me at{' '}
      <a href="mailto:hello@creativenux.com">hello@creativenux.com</a>, or find me on{' '}
      <a href="https://x.com/creativenux" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        X.com
      </a>
      {' '}and{' '}
      <a href="https://github.com/creativenux" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        GitHub
      </a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
